    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074779_28_3599-3664",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "3599-3664",
      "markText": "他身体中有一团密云。这时布里蒙达说了声，过来。“七个太阳”巴尔塔萨的意志脱离了肉体，但没有升上星空，因为它属于大地，属于布里蒙达。",
      "totalCount": 416,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074779&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=3599&rangeEnd=3664",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/79832b50813ab83b5g019696?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=3599&rangeEnd=3664"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074779_4_2002-2011",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2002-2011",
      "markText": "水罐正等着甘泉呢。",
      "totalCount": 360,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074779&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2002&rangeEnd=2011",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/79832b50813ab83b5g019696?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2002&rangeEnd=2011"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074779_3_941-1017",
      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "941-1017",
      "markText": "当我断言现实——这个漂浮不定的概念——对于存在的尽可能准确的了解，是我们与超越现实的事物的接触点以及通向那些事物的道路时，我知道我陷入了无从解释的境地。",
      "totalCount": 345,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074779&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=941&rangeEnd=1017",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/79832b50813ab83b5g019696?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=941&rangeEnd=1017"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074779_4_2717-2766",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2717-2766",
      "markText": "但没人明白究竟谁要接受考验，是上帝本身，是安多尼修士的品德，是国王的能力，还是王后不佳的生育能力。",
      "totalCount": 330,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074779&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2717&rangeEnd=2766",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/79832b50813ab83b5g019696?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2717&rangeEnd=2766"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074779_4_2438-2527",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "2438-2527",
      "markText": "国王又问，你是怎么知道的；安多尼修士说，我知道，但不知道是如何知道的，真谛不过是借我之口传达，信仰无须回答更多，请陛下建造修道院吧，不久便会有子嗣，要是不肯修建，上帝会做出裁定。",
      "totalCount": 273,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074779&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2438&rangeEnd=2527",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/79832b50813ab83b5g019696?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=2438&rangeEnd=2527"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074779_4_1899-1930",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "1899-1930",
      "markText": "还有一些人，他们既不知道该做什么，也不明白自己为什么身在此处。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074779&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1899&rangeEnd=1930",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/79832b50813ab83b5g019696?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=1899&rangeEnd=1930"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074779_22_14188-14234",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "14188-14234",
      "markText": "魔鬼正在这谷地上方观看，对自己的善良和慈悲感到惊愕，他从来不承想在他的地狱里实施这样的酷刑。",
      "totalCount": 252,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074779&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=14188&rangeEnd=14234",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/79832b50813ab83b5g019696?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=14188&rangeEnd=14234"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074779_4_902-912",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "902-912",
      "markText": "不过，上帝是伟大的。",
      "totalCount": 240,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074779&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=902&rangeEnd=912",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/79832b50813ab83b5g019696?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=902&rangeEnd=912"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074779_4_507-536",
      "chapterUid": 4,
      "range": "507-536",
      "markText": "这首先因为，无生育能力不是男人们的病症，而是女人们的缺陷，",
      "totalCount": 231,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300074779&chapterUid=4&rangeStart=507&rangeEnd=536",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/79832b50813ab83b5g019696?chapterUid=4&rangeStart=507&rangeEnd=536"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300074779_17_5335-5432",
